Significant modifications include:
- Modernized dependencies (Ruby 3.x, latest gems)
- Replaced multi_json with oj for better performance
- Updated TLS minimum version from 1.1 to 1.2
- Improved error handling and logging
- Updated to work with latest Fluentd versions (1.16+)
- Code refactoring for Ruby 3.x compatibility
- Enhanced test coverage and CI/CD
